<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Joseph Chiu — Meet Me</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&family=Lato:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body {
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    background: #0A1F44;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: flex-start;
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 32px 16px;
  }
  .brochure {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 1080px;
    min-height: 860px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  }
  .panel { padding: 30px 24px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
  .panel-left { background: #0D2B6B; color: #EEF4FF; }
  .panel-center { background: #F0F6FF; color: #0D2B6B; border-left: 1px solid #BDD0F0; border-right: 1px solid #BDD0F0; }
  .panel-right { background: #1A4A9C; color: #EEF4FF; }

  .serif { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; }

  .profile-photo {
    width: 130px; height: 130px; border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover; object-position: center;
    border: 3px solid #5B9BF5;
    display: block; margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .photo-rect {
    width: 100%; height: 180px;
    object-fit: cover; border-radius: 8px;
    display: block;
  }

  .big-name {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 26px; font-weight: 700;
    color: #EEF4FF; line-height: 1.15; text-align: center;
  }
  .tagline {
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #7EB8FF; text-align: center;
  }
  .divider { height: 1px; background: #5B9BF5; opacity: 0.35; width: 100%; }
  .divider-dark { height: 1px; background: #5B9BF5; opacity: 0.25; width: 100%; }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #7EB8FF; margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .section-title-dark {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #1A4A9C; margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .body-text { font-size: 12.5px; line-height: 1.65; color: #C8DEFF; }
  .body-text-dark { font-size: 12.5px; line-height: 1.65; color: #1A3A70; }

  .quote-block {
    border-left: 3px solid #5B9BF5; padding: 8px 12px;
    background: rgba(91,155,245,0.1); border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
  }
  .quote-text {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-style: italic;
    font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6; color: #EEF4FF;
  }

  .tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 4px; }
  .tag {
    background: rgba(91,155,245,0.18); border: 0.5px solid #5B9BF5;
    color: #7EB8FF; font-size: 10.5px; padding: 3px 9px; border-radius: 20px;
  }

  .goal-card {
    background: rgba(91,155,245,0.1); border: 0.5px solid rgba(91,155,245,0.35);
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 12px;
  }
  .goal-card-light {
    background: #DCE9FF; border: 0.5px solid #5B9BF5;
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px 12px;
  }
  .goal-label { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #7EB8FF; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .goal-label-dark { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #1A4A9C; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .goal-text { font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5; color: #C8DEFF; }
  .goal-text-dark { font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5; color: #0D2B6B; }

  .from-badge {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
    background: #DCE9FF; border-radius: 20px; padding: 5px 12px;
    width: fit-content; margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .from-badge span { font-size: 12px; color: #0D2B6B; font-weight: 700; }

  .fun-fact {
    background: rgba(91,155,245,0.12); border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 9px 12px; border-left: 3px solid #5B9BF5;
  }
  .fun-fact-label { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #7EB8FF; margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .fun-fact-text { font-size: 12px; color: #C8DEFF; line-height: 1.5; }

  .explore-item { display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: flex-start; }
  .explore-icon {
    width: 30px; height: 30px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(91,155,245,0.2); border: 0.5px solid #5B9BF5;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0; font-size: 14px;
  }
  .explore-name { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: #EEF4FF; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .explore-desc { font-size: 11px; line-height: 1.5; color: #A0C4FF; }

  .center-big {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700; color: #0D2B6B; line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .italic-note {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 11px;
    font-style: italic; color: #A0C4FF; text-align: center;
  }

  @media print {
    body { background: white; padding: 0; }
    .brochure { box-shadow: none; max-width: 100%; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="brochure">

  <!-- LEFT: About Me -->
  <div class="panel panel-left">
    <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Joseph Chiu" class="profile-photo">

    <div>
      <div class="big-name">Joseph Chiu</div>
      <div class="tagline" style="margin-top:6px">Pre-Dental &middot; Biologist &middot; Creator</div>
    </div>

    <div class="from-badge">
      <span>📍 Fremont, California</span>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div>
      <div class="section-title">Hobbies &amp; Interests</div>
      <div class="tags" style="margin-top:6px">
        <span class="tag">📸 Photography</span>
        <span class="tag">🎬 Video Editing</span>
        <span class="tag">🏊 Swimming</span>
        <span class="tag">🤽 Water Polo</span>
        <span class="tag">🌿 Outdoors</span>
        <span class="tag">🍜 Eating</span>
        <span class="tag">👥 Hanging Out</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="fun-fact">
      <div class="fun-fact-label">⚡ Fun Fact</div>
      <div class="fun-fact-text">I trained in Taekwondo for <strong style="color:#7EB8FF">13 years</strong> — discipline that carried over into everything I do.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div>
      <div class="section-title">Favorite Quote</div>
      <div class="quote-block" style="margin-top:6px">
        <div class="quote-text">"I've failed over and over and over again in my life. And that is why I succeed."</div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;color:#7EB8FF;margin-top:6px">— Michael Jordan</div>
      </div>
      <div class="body-text" style="margin-top:8px;font-size:11.5px;">In swimming and water polo, I failed constantly — missed times, missed goals. But I kept going. That's what this quote means to me.</div>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top:auto">
      <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Joseph competing in a swim race" class="photo-rect">
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CENTER: Upcoming Plans -->
  <div class="panel panel-center">
    <div style="text-align:center">
      <div class="section-title-dark" style="text-align:center;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:2px">Upcoming Plans</div>
      <div class="center-big">What's Next<br>for Joseph</div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="section-title-dark">Where I'll Be</div>
      <div class="body-text-dark">Commuting to <strong>San José State University (SJSU)</strong> next fall — living at home in Fremont and making the drive to campus every day.</div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="section-title-dark">What I'm Studying</div>
      <div class="body-text-dark"><strong>Biology</strong> on a <strong>pre-dental track.</strong> Fascinated by the intersection of science and hands-on patient care — dental school is the goal I'm building toward one class at a time.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="divider-dark"></div>

    <div class="goal-card-light">
      <div class="goal-label-dark">🎯 Short-Term Goal (1–2 years)</div>
      <div class="goal-text-dark">Transfer to a UC campus. If that path shifts, secure a job to save money, land a dental internship, and log real hands-on clinical hours to strengthen my application.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="goal-card-light">
      <div class="goal-label-dark">🌟 Long-Term Goal (3–5 years)</div>
      <div class="goal-text-dark">Earn my bachelor's and continue into dental school — ideally University of the Pacific (UOP). I want to become a dentist who genuinely connects with patients.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="divider-dark"></div>

    <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Dental student in clinical setting" class="photo-rect" style="margin-top:auto">

    <div style="text-align:center">
      <div style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:11px;font-style:italic;color:#1A4A9C">Let's connect if you're at SJSU or on the pre-dental path!</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- RIGHT: Things to Explore -->
  <div class="panel panel-right">
    <div>
      <div class="tagline" style="margin-bottom:6px">San José &amp; Beyond</div>
      <div class="serif" style="font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:#EEF4FF;line-height:1.2">Things I Want<br>to Explore</div>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="explore-item">
      <div class="explore-icon">🍜</div>
      <div>
        <div class="explore-name">The Hole-in-the-Wall Food Scene</div>
        <div class="explore-desc">Story Rd's Vietnamese corridor and hidden Japanese spots near Japantown. I want the best bún bò Huế and mochi the tourist guides skip.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="explore-item">
      <div class="explore-icon">🌿</div>
      <div>
        <div class="explore-name">Hidden Creek Trails</div>
        <div class="explore-desc">Almaden Quicksilver and Calero Reservoir trails are underrated. I want to hike every loop and find the overlook spots locals keep to themselves — camera in hand.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="explore-item">
      <div class="explore-icon">🎵</div>
      <div>
        <div class="explore-name">SJ's Underground Live Music</div>
        <div class="explore-desc">Small jazz bars and open-mic nights almost no one knows about. I want to find and document them photographically and on video.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="explore-item">
      <div class="explore-icon">🏯</div>
      <div>
        <div class="explore-name">Japantown's Living History</div>
        <div class="explore-desc">One of only 3 remaining Japantowns in the US. I want to learn its WWII history, visit cultural centers, and shoot a photo series on what it looks like today.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="explore-item">
      <div class="explore-icon">🚌</div>
      <div>
        <div class="explore-name">Mastering the VTA &amp; Caltrain</div>
        <div class="explore-desc">Commuting from Fremont — I want every transit hack: fastest Caltrain+VTA combos, free parking spots, and how to get anywhere in the South Bay car-free.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="divider" style="margin-top:auto"></div>

    <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="San José Japantown pagoda at dusk" class="photo-rect">

    <div class="italic-note">If you know a hidden gem in SJ,<br>please tell me immediately.</div>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
